data.revised_prompt: A delightful and endearing depiction of a baby sea otter. This petite, fluffy entity is elegantly floating on its back, with its small webbed paws folded charmingly over its fuzzy abdomen. It has large, spherical, innocent-looking eyes that radiate youthful curiosity. As it blissfully floats on the serene, glistening ocean surface under the radiance of the golden sunset, it playfully tosses a shiny seashell from one paw to the other, exemplifying its playful and uniquely otter-like behavior.
